                </p>
                <p align="justify">
                    + You will not be refunded the goods after the payment has been completed.
                </p>

                <p align="justify">
                    <font style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(255, 0, 255);">Not returnable</font>
                </p>
                <p align="justify">
                    In any school after completing the delivery and payment of the purchase, we do not accept the exchange or return of the goods as payment has been completed to the factory.
