                    In case the product has lost its packaging, is not intact or damaged due to customer error, Studionoithat.com has the right to refuse the above return.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tab-pane fade" id="tab-bh">
                <p>
                    <strong>Warranty period according to factory regulations</strong>
                </p>
