                    a. Broken due to design or manufacturing defect. No warranty if the product is used for the wrong purpose.
                </p>
                <p>
                    b. Paint is peeling because it doesn't stick to the wood.
                </p>
                <p>
                    c. The product is eaten by termites from the inside of the wood.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>Warranty Method</strong>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Depending on the level of damage, we will proceed in the order of priority as follows:
                </p>
                <p>
                    1. Paint miles, repair, reinforce products: done within 1 week
                </p>
                <p>
                    2. Exchange similar products: within 2 weeks if the product is available in stock on the web.
                </p>
                <p>
                    3. Product refund excluding shipping fee: made within 1 month from the date of notification of no stock for replacement.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>Warranty Procedure</strong>
                </p>
                <p>
                    1. Contact the sales department to provide the following information: contact information, damaged error, order number.
                </p>
                <p>
                    2. The product is only warranted at the factory. We will arrange an appointment to receive the product for warranty within 7 days. We do not bear the cost of shipping and receiving warranty products. Shipping costs are calculated according to the standard delivery shipping policy.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

